query:
INSERT INTO characterItems (id, name, imageUrl, rarity, itemType, coinCost, createdAt)
SELECT id, name, imageUrl, rarity, itemType, 0, createdAt FROM gachaItems
ON DUPLICATE KEY UPDATE 
  name = VALUES(name),
  imageUrl = VALUES(imageUrl),
  rarity = VALUES(rarity),
  itemType = VALUES(itemType)
